    <text>
        <body><div type="bibliography">
                
                <p><bibl>Morelli in <ptr target="#SECir"/>, <citedRange>227a</citedRange> (no image)</bibl>;
                    <bibl><ptr target="#IGCyr"/> <citedRange>103315</citedRange></bibl>.
                    Cf. <bibl><ptr target="#cdl2000"/>, pp. <citedRange>15, 73, 227</citedRange></bibl>;
                    <bibl><ptr target="#parisipresicce2007a"/>, p.<citedRange>498</citedRange></bibl>.</p>
            </div><div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" xml:space="preserve">
                
                         <ab>
                             <lb n="1"/><persName type="divine" ref="#Curete"><name nymRef="#Κωρής"><expan><abbr>Κωρ</abbr><ex>ῆτος</ex></expan></name></persName>
                         </ab>
            </div><div type="apparatus" xml:space="preserve">
            
                <p/>
               </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="fr">
            <p><supplied reason="subaudible">Autel du</supplied> <expan><abbr>Kour</abbr><ex>ète</ex></expan>.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="en">
            <p><supplied reason="subaudible">Altar of the</supplied> <expan><abbr>Cur</abbr><ex>ete</ex></expan>.</p>
                </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="it">
            <p><supplied reason="subaudible">Altare del</supplied> <expan><abbr>Cur</abbr><ex>ete</ex></expan>.</p>
            </div><div type="commentary">
                
                <p>The script shows clearly that this mention was inscribed later than <ref type="inscription" source="#IGCyr2">IGCyr103310</ref> (<foreign xml:lang="la">contra</foreign> Morelli).</p>
                <p>On this altar two deities were worshipped and possibly separately, as their names were inscribed on two different sides of the block.</p>
                <p>This inscription was erroneously collected twice in the first edition; the other entry, under number <ref type="inscription" source="#IGCyr">IGCyr006600</ref>, has now been deleted.</p>
            </div></body>
    </text>
